data.description: **PRICE REDUCTION** Welcome home to 3037 Sutton Woods Dr, Plant City, FL 33566 – a 4-bed, 2-bath haven where modern luxury meets energy efficiency. Fully renovated with high-end finishes, this home features a chef's kitchen, open-concept living, and a master suite retreat. Outside, a large screened-in pool offers a personal oasis for relaxation and entertainment. The property stands out with a fully paid-off solar system, ensuring both environmental consciousness and long-term cost savings. This residence at 3037 Sutton Woods Dr is not just a home; it's a lifestyle. Contact us for a private viewing and to learn more about all the other benefits this home has to offer.
